{"tid":1947550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<識玩> 台北歡迎被北京驅逐的美國傳媒記者到台灣設駐點","createTime":"2020-03-28T11:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T12:10:31.000Z","uid":227801,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6701005bd7173129612bf54c6803284ef970761d","tid":1947550,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517436-20200328.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517436-20200328.htm&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=d557dcf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517436-20200328.htm&h=d0ad6c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517436-20200328.htm</a><br />\n在台北，外交部長吳釗燮表示，歡迎被北京當局驅逐的三間美國傳媒機構駐京記者，到台灣設立駐點。<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮在社交網站表示，當《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》及《華盛頓郵報》的傳媒朋友，在大陸面臨日益增高的敵意時，歡迎他們轉到台灣這個自由民主燈塔的地方，又說民眾會張開雙臂，以真誠笑容歡迎他們。<br />\n<br />\n北京早前要求這三間傳媒年底前記者證到期的美籍記者交還記者證，今後不得在中國包括港澳地區繼續從事記者工作。三間傳媒其後發表聲明，呼籲當局收回決定，但被外交部提出嚴正交涉。"},{"pid":"b2bd61397403966430823c060b842cafc9caac91","tid":1947550,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb24ac5e944e582bb83d4b82b81015b908b54a16","tid":1947550,"uid":293741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"人棄我取 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff84fd024b95fc093a22864760e7dd30bef11cb","tid":1947550,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f724fd49d4f2d2afd1aff7b4e4a1faaee61b4d07","tid":1947550,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb24ac5e944e582bb83d4b82b81015b908b54a16","tid":1947